{
  "stem": "12052.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I got befriended with people who were also from outside, Polish people.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "While I learned in between the Polish language pretty fluent.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And sometimes I ran the shifts for them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They didn't show up.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They told me, I don't show up.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So actually, shift was a 12 hour shift, seven days a week.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I-- I ran-- I ran his shift, and he brought me a piece of bacon and a piece of bread.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this was heaven on Earth to-- to receive a piece of bread and a piece of bacon.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that was like raw bacon, and you just slice it and eat it with the bread like-- like a delicacy.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I-- I developed a very good relation with with-- with the people who worked there, with the machinist.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then I ran different kind of machinery in-- in Czestochowa.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And my father worked like a foreman.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He-- he was a big, strong man, and he spoke fluent German, and so forth.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Well, he came from a region where they spoke German, when there was Austria and Hungary.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he was, most time, foreman.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- and he had a good job.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I had a good job.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we were pretty still strong in comparing to.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We had all the chances to survive the war, until again, the front advanced.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And-- Let's stop for a minute and go back, still, to your living conditions, then, at Czestochowa.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Were you in-- were you with your father?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was with my father in a camp.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we-- the sleeping conditions there were very bad.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was a barrack with, I don't know, there were like very, very narrow-- narrow quarters, and cold.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, in winter, it's below zero.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And you had only one blanket there.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
